WEBVTT

00:00:29.996 --> 00:00:31.524
one on either side.

00:00:32.354 --> 00:00:35.822
That was the first time
I understood viscerally --

00:00:35.846 --> 00:00:38.243
just for a fleeting moment --

00:00:38.267 --> 00:00:40.235
what incarceration might feel like.

00:00:40.886 --> 00:00:44.887
And I promised myself all those years ago
as a young, public defender

00:00:44.911 --> 00:00:47.529
that I would never,
ever forget that feeling.

00:00:48.277 --> 00:00:49.659
And I never have.

00:00:50.024 --> 00:00:53.975
It inspired me to fight for each
and every one of my clients' freedom

00:00:53.999 --> 00:00:56.131
as if it was my own.

00:00:57.142 --> 00:00:58.468
Freedom.

00:00:58.832 --> 00:01:02.175
A concept so fundamental
to the American psyche